Acknowledgments

wick_agent's architecture is inspired by langchain-ai/deepagents
(https://github.com/langchain-ai/deepagents), specifically its approach to
middleware-style hook points around the agent loop, planning via a todo list,
sub-agent delegation, and persistent memory injection. wick_agent is an
independent implementation — no source code has been copied — but credit is
due for the architectural ideas.

